D(future_labor‚Üídebt): Money enters as debt, creating structural unpayability. Future labor denominated as obligation collapses action space before conscious choice. The quantification of time-to-come as owed.

O(metrics‚Üíidentity): Net worth, ratings, scores become proxy-selves. Metrics fuse with identity, escalating exit costs into existential threat. Who you are becomes what you measure.

D(clock‚Üíurgency): Clock time compresses embodied rhythm. Standardized temporal enforcement manufactures urgency independent of task demands. Fire becomes external compulsion.

O(comparison‚Üífragmentation): Comparison metrics prune relational fields. Lateral bonds severed, solidarity networks fragmented into competitive rankings. Water severed by ranking.

X(metabolic_collapse‚Üíno_refusal): Metabolic capacity drops below threshold for refusal. Health consequences accumulate as unrecoverable damage. Exhaustion regenerates loop by eliminating energy for alternatives. Z-collapse at X.

